CREATE TABLE etl_output_db.load_clean
WITH (
    format = 'PARQUET',
    external_location = 's3://your-bucket/load_clean/'
) AS
SELECT
    CAST(passengerid AS INT) AS passengerid,
    CAST(survived AS INT) AS survived,
    CAST(pclass AS INT) AS pclass,
    name,
    sex,
    CAST(age AS FLOAT) AS age,
    CAST(sibsp AS INT) AS sibsp,
    CAST(parch AS INT) AS parch,
    ticket,
    CAST(fare AS FLOAT) AS fare,
    cabin,
    embarked
FROM etl_output_db.load
DESCRIBE load

CREATE TABLE etl_output_db.load_clean
